ir John Wallace 7th of Riccarton est né en 1345, à Craigie, Ayrshire, Écosse, son père, John Wallace 6th Riccarton, avait 38 ans et sa mère, Lady Margaret de Lindsay Countess of Craigie, avait 35 ans. Il a épousé Margaret Douglas en 1373, à Craigie, Ayrshire, Écosse. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils. Il est décédé en 1409, à Paisley, Renfrewshire, Écosse, à l’âge de 64 ans."},"de":{"1345–1409":"1345–1409","1331–1378":"1331–1378","1340–1409":"1340–1409","1355–1409":"1355–1409","1360–Male":"1360–Verstorben","1340–1425":"1340–1425","1375–1407":"1375–1407","1377–Male":"1377–Verstorben","1307–1377":"1307–1377","1310–1372":"1310–1372","1330":"1330","1373":"1373","1340":"1340","1372":"1372","1360":"1360","1425":"1425","1345":"1345","before 30 June 1407":"vor 30. Juni 1407","1378":"1378","1377":"1377","1355":"1355","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","1331":"1331","1409":"1409","1407":"1407","1307":"1307","Craigie, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Craigie, Ayrshire, Scotland","Craigie Castle, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Craigie, Ayrshire, Scotland","Paisley, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Paisley, Renfrewshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","lifeSummary":"Als Sir John Wallace 7th of Riccarton 1345 in Craigie, Ayrshire, Scotland geboren wurde, war sein Vater John Wallace 6th Riccarton 38 und seine Mutter Lady Margaret de Lindsay Countess of Craigie 35. Er hat 1373 in Craigie, Ayrshire, Scotland Margaret Douglas geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne. Er starb 1409 im Alter von 64 Jahren in Paisley, Renfrewshire, Scotland."},"ht":{"1345–1409":"1345–1409","1331–1378":"1331–1378","1340–1409":"1340–1409","1355–1409":"1355–1409","1360–Male":"1360–Desede","1340–1425":"1340–1425","1375–1407":"1375–1407","1377–Male":"1377–Desede","1307–1377":"1307–1377","1310–1372":"1310–1372","1330":"1330","1373":"1373","1340":"1340","1372":"1372","1360":"1360","1425":"1425","1345":"1345","before 30 June 1407":"before 30 June 1407","1378":"1378","1377":"1377","1355":"1355","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","1331":"1331","1409":"1409","14